OL,3,CThe Minab school attack has scarred
OL,4,CIran - and it will not be forgiven
OL,6,FWhen they went to school, there was no
OL,7,Fwar. Their deaths marked the start of
OL,8,Fit and they never came home.
OL,9,FInternational Editor Emma Murphy
OL,10,Fspeaks to the mothers of Minab, whose
OL,11,Fchildren were killed on the first day
OL,12,Fof the war in Iran.
OL,14,FI don't speak Farsi but a shared
OL,15,Flanguage wasn't needed to understand
OL,16,Fthe pain of the mothers whose children
OL,17,Fdied in the attack on their school in
OL,18,FMinab.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
