OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784249267
OL,3,CThe Minab school attack has scarred
OL,4,CIran - and it will not be forgiven
OL,6,FEach held onto the photographs of the
OL,7,Fchild, children or sisters they had
OL,8,Flost. In death, they held those photos
OL,9,Fas tightly as they would have held
OL,10,Fonto their loved ones' hands in life.
OL,12,FThe agony they have endured since
OL,13,FFebruary was etched on their faces and
OL,14,Fso clear in their eyes it was almost
OL,15,Funbearable to witness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
