CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784249267
OL,3,CThe Minab school attack has scarred
OL,4,CIran - and it will not be forgiven
OL,6,FNot all the mothers were able to speak
OL,7,Fwith us, but they wished to be part of
OL,8,Fthe interview. Some sat in silence
OL,9,Flooking at their child's image, others
OL,10,Fsobbed behind us as they heard the
OL,11,Ftestimonies of those who, at that
OL,12,Fmoment, had the strength to speak
OL,13,Fabout their loss.
OL,15,FI will never forget the pain in that
OL,16,Froom.
OL,18,FMasoumeh Esmaili's 12-year-old
OL,19,Fdaughter was killed on February 28
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
