OL,3,CThe Minab school attack has scarred
OL,4,CIran - and it will not be forgiven
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FTheir children died on the first day
OL,12,Fof the war, February 28, when American
OL,13,Fmissiles hit their school. The US
OL,14,Fauthorities have offered differing
OL,15,Fexplanations for what went on and
OL,16,Flaunched an investigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
