PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784249267
OL,3,CThe Minab school attack has scarred
OL,4,CIran - and it will not be forgiven
OL,6,FWhatever its outcome, nothing will
OL,7,Fchange and there is no belief there
OL,8,Fwill be an honest account of what
OL,9,Fhappened, whether deliberate or
OL,10,Faccidental. The nearly 200 children
OL,11,Fand teachers the Tomahawk missiles
OL,12,Fkilled were not part of this war but
OL,13,Fit took their lives.
OL,15,FThat morning these mothers had gone
OL,16,Fthrough the same routine as mothers
OL,17,Facross the world, hurrying their
OL,18,Fchildren out to school, some late,
OL,19,Fsome forgetting things, some just
OL,20,Fcalmly heading off for another day in
OL,21,Fclass.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
