OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784249267
OL,3,CThe Minab school attack has scarred
OL,4,CIran - and it will not be forgiven
OL,6,FWhen they went to school there was no
OL,7,Fwar. Their deaths marked the start of
OL,8,Fit and they never came home.
OL,10,FThe children had only been at school a
OL,11,Ffew hours when the war began. Parents
OL,12,Fhad been called to come and collect
OL,13,Ftheir children even though there was
OL,14,Fno sign of any attacks near them.
OL,16,FFatemeh Halafzadeh's 13-year-old
OL,17,Fdaughter was killed in the strike
OL,19,FThey were on the way when the
OL,20,Fexplosions happened.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784249267
OL,3,CThe Minab school attack has scarred
OL,4,CIran - and it will not be forgiven
OL,6,FMinab is not a big place and every
OL,7,Fparent heard them, they were already
OL,8,Frushing to the school but didn't
OL,9,Fconsider that it would be hit. When
OL,10,Fthey arrived they found it in ruins
OL,11,Fand their children in the rubble.
OL,13,FThe descriptions of how they found
OL,14,Ftheir children and what they were able
OL,15,Fto retrieve is too graphic to share.
OL,16,FSome of the parents who got there
OL,17,Fquicker were themselves caught in the
OL,18,Fattack.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
