PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784249267
OL,3,CThe Minab school attack has scarred
OL,4,CIran - and it will not be forgiven
OL,6,FThe impact of that attack on this war
OL,7,Fand on this country cannot be
OL,8,Funderestimated. Pretty much everywhere
OL,9,Fwe have been on this trip and the
OL,10,Flast, there are images of the
OL,11,Fchildren. Most people we have
OL,12,Finterviewed speak of what happened,
OL,13,Fwith outrage, with sadness and with a
OL,14,Fsense of fury that will endure long
OL,15,Fafter this war ends.
OL,17,FMinab will be a scar forever etched in
OL,18,Fthis country's soul and will not be
OL,19,Fforgiven.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
